  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282460/extras/a81c137600b6710555d5a4edf2208420.avif?t=1733771931\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a serene Mediterranean island where the <strong>worlds of the  land and sea intertwine</strong>. Embark on a heart-warming, epic journey to help a mysterious girl from the sea find her way home. 🏝️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Having always felt adrift in your own life,  you'll meet enigmatic characters who will not only help you unearth the island's rich mythology, but unlock hidden truths within yourself! 🔍</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This fresh take on a visual novel features <strong>breath-taking artwork and music that will move you to tears</strong>, so what are you waiting for? Come and join Ayasal on a poignant adventure that you will carry in your heart forever! 💙 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Special Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗣️ Change how characters see you with dialogue choices and branching paths</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐚 Hidden collectables to find throughout</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🖼️ A gallery featuring unlockable concept art</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 Mysterious achievements to uncover</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦀 A lovely crab-friend called Marvin:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282460/extras/f60b1b7aa5f3de39ad3fdd01273234c0.poster.avif?t=1733771931\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282460/extras/f60b1b7aa5f3de39ad3fdd01273234c0.webm?t=1733771931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282460/extras/f60b1b7aa5f3de39ad3fdd01273234c0.mp4?t=1733771931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282460/extras/a81c137600b6710555d5a4edf2208420.avif?t=1733771931\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a serene Mediterranean island where the <strong>worlds of the  land and sea intertwine</strong>. Embark on a heart-warming, epic journey to help a mysterious girl from the sea find her way home. 🏝️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Having always felt adrift in your own life,  you'll meet enigmatic characters who will not only help you unearth the island's rich mythology, but unlock hidden truths within yourself! 🔍</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This fresh take on a visual novel features <strong>breath-taking artwork and music that will move you to tears</strong>, so what are you waiting for? Come and join Ayasal on a poignant adventure that you will carry in your heart forever! 💙 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Special Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗣️ Change how characters see you with dialogue choices and branching paths</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐚 Hidden collectables to find throughout</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🖼️ A gallery featuring unlockable concept art</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 Mysterious achievements to uncover</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦀 A lovely crab-friend called Marvin:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282460/extras/f60b1b7aa5f3de39ad3fdd01273234c0.poster.avif?t=1733771931\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282460/extras/f60b1b7aa5f3de39ad3fdd01273234c0.webm?t=1733771931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282460/extras/f60b1b7aa5f3de39ad3fdd01273234c0.mp4?t=1733771931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
